       <div id="binary fussion">
    BINARY FUSSION<br>
    </h3>
Binary Fussion simply means when a single parent e.g Amoeba ,wants to reproduce it will start to have an out growth 
on the body which gradually deviates from the body forming a new organism.<br><br>
Study The Diagram Below:<br><br><br><br>
<img src="https://cdn1.byjus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/binary-fission-in-amoeba.png" alt="diagram of binary fussion in amoeba" />
</h2> 
</em>This image showed the processes of thr Amoeba binary fission<br><br><br><br>
