    <div id="conjugation">
   <p><h3>Conjugation </h3>
This can be defined as the process by which two parent of a single cell organism lies together each on there side and slowly develops an out
growth which later joins with the other parent outgrowth. This tube serves as a host in other to transfer gamet for a parent to the other to form a zygospore   ,e.g spirogyra.<br><br>The Diagram below Shows conjugation in spirogyra<br><br><br><br>
